name: The Universe Inside Us
description:
Like roses have thorns we have many shapes
We can go trough all the figures.
We can hondulate on time.
We can just be.
We can be named: the iris of the world.
Just like things, they die and reborn,
Just like a hug we interwine in space, the cosmos.
We don't need a suitcase with our third eye wide open... 
We are the cosmic travelers!




Collaborative nft piece with @InmateriaTravel (Check his stuff on HEN and social medias)
